      "  Data: `processSteps: [{label:'Raw footage',icon:'\u{1F3AC}'},{label:'AI polish',icon:'\u2728'},{label:'Export',icon:'\u{1F680}'}]`",
      "- `collapse`: Shrinking bars/tabs animating into a single final output card. Visual metaphor for 'consolidate' / 'one place'.",
      "  Data: `headline: 'All of it. One place.'`",
